n-h%C3%A0nh-dinh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-c%C3%BAc-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-h%E1%BB%B1u-ph%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-C9-d7ihigmZpe20PKmNQYQ">Hoạ tham tán đại thần hành dinh thưởng cúc thập vịnh hựu phú thập vịnh kỳ 09 - 和參贊大臣行營賞菊十詠又賦十詠其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Long-H%C3%A0m-nham-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-1GazVumHT_GZZJJ358kJJA">Long Hàm nham tức sự - 龍頷岩即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-33/poem-0m6N_pBBc6VkaZEtpd4TUg">Thủ 33 - 首33</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Vi%C3%AAn-trang-v%C3%A3n-di%E1%BB%83u-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-cZmYtqWVrKSZRudchK25pQ">Viên trang vãn diểu tức sự - 園莊晚眺即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
